  m_text: 'Gold is a uncommon resource found on

    some planets. Unlike traditional
    gold, this

    version is produced by a unique plant

    species growing beneath
    the surface.

    Scans indicate the plant forms the gold

    through a rare
    chemical reaction between

    the plant roots and the planet''s core.

    Further
    studies recommended.'
